==治療==
狄奎凡氏症治療較多是以醫學常規為主，較少科学数据基礎，這點和其他肌肉骨骼類的疾病類似。在1895年首次提出此一疾病後，一直到1955年Jarrod Ismond才提出注射皮质类固醇的治療方式<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite journal | date = Jun 1955 | title = Local hydrocortisone in de Quervain's disease | url = | journal = Br Med J | volume = 1 | issue = 4929| pages = 1501–3 | doi=10.1136/bmj.1.4929.1501}}</ref>，在這以前，手術似乎是唯一的治療方式<ref name="ReferenceA" /><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Piver JD, Raney RB | date = Mar 1952 | title = De Quervain's tendovaginitis | url = | journal = Am J Surg | volume = 83 | issue = 5| pages = 691–4 | doi=10.1016/0002-9610(52)90304-8}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Lamphier TA, Long NG, Dennehy T | date = Dec 1953 | title = De Quervain's disease: an analysis of 52 cases | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-surgery_1953-12_138_6/page/832| journal = Ann Surg | volume = 138 | issue = 6| pages = 832–41 }}</ref>。McKenzie在1972年時提出應該以注射皮质类固醇為第一線治療，若注射治療不成功才接受手術，這也是後來普遍接受的作法<ref>{{cite journal | author = McKenzie JM | date = Dec 1972 | title = Conservative treatment of de Quervain's disease | url = | journal = Br Med J | volume = 4 | issue = 5841| pages = 659–60 | doi=10.1136/bmj.4.5841.659}}</ref>。在2013年發表的系統性評論及元分析指出，皮质类固醇注射是對狄奎凡氏症保守性治療的一種有效方式，約對50%的病患有效，不過還需要更多有關临床益处的研究<ref name=Ashraf2013>{{cite journal|last=Ashraf|first=MO|author2=Devadoss, VG|title=Systematic review and meta-analysis on steroid injection therapy for de Quervain's tenosynovitis in adults|journal=European journal of orthopaedic surgery & traumatology: orthopedie traumatologie|date=22 January 2013|pmid=23412309|doi=10.1007/s00590-012-1164-z|volume=24|issue=2|pages=149–57}}</ref>。有關治療有效性的数据相对较少，目前也還不確定在狄奎凡氏症的[[病程|病程]]中是否會有幫助{{Medical citation needed}}。

姑息性治療包括固定腕部，並且將拇指固定在指間關節位置的夾板，以及消炎藥物或是對乙酰氨基酚。系統分析及元分析不支持夾板配合類固醇注射一起使用<ref name=Cochrane2009>{{cite journal|last=Peters-Veluthamaningal|first=C|author2=van der Windt, DA |author3=Winters, JC |author4=Meyboom-de Jong, B |title=Corticosteroid injection for de Quervain's tenosynovitis|journal=The Cochrane database of systematic reviews|date=8 July 2009|issue=3|pages=CD005616|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005616.pub2|pmid=19588376}}</ref><ref name=Coldham2006>{{cite journal|last=Coldham|first=F|title=The use of splinting in the non-surgical treatment of De Quervains disease: a review of the literature|journal=British Journal of Hand Therapy|year=2006|volume=11|issue=2|pages=48–55|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMH0023405/|accessdate=8 December 2013|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017204849/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMH0023405/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

假若病患第一間隔區的滑膜鞘可以縱向打開，手術可以減緩大部份的病情<ref name="ReferenceB">{{cite journal | author = Weiss AP, Akelman E, Tabatabai M | date = Jul 1994 | title = Treatment of de Quervain's disease | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-hand-surgery_1994-07_19a_4/page/595| journal = J Hand Surg [Am] | volume = 19 | issue = 4| pages = 595–8 }}</ref>，其中最大的風險是可能影響橈骨感覺神經。

有些物理治療師及職能治療師認為，狄奎凡氏症是因為提昇重物時重複性的使用拇指而造成，有些活動會讓病情惡化，而訓練其他部份的肌肉，避免過度使用拇指會對病情有幫助，因此物理／職能治療師會建議使用其他的提昇重物方式。建議避免從事一些活動，並且進行一些肌肉強化的運動，訓練其他部位，不會過度刺激拇指的肌腱。

有些物理治療師及職能治療師會根據一些治療方式可減輕炎症和疼痛并促進癒合的基本原理，將這些治療方式和治療性運動合併使用，其中包括有UST、[[短波熱療|短波熱療]]（SWD）及其他的深層熱治療，也包括{{le|經皮神經電刺激|Transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation}}、[[針灸|針灸]]、紅外線療法或是{{le|低能量靜脈雷射|cold laser}}治療。不過此疾病在病理學下不是滑膜鞘的發炎性變化，發炎是因為摩擦產生的繼發性症狀<ref>Eplasty. 2013; 13: ic52.</ref>。讓病患減輕其繼發性的發炎對真正的病因幫助不大，不過可能可以減輕疼痛，讓病患比較可以進行一些有治療性的運動。

在注射藥物或是進行手術前先進行物理治療，可以減少病患的花費，也是治療許多肌肉骨骼受傷的可行作法。
==社會文化==
黑莓拇指（BlackBerry thumb）是[[新词|新词]]，是指因經常用拇指按[[PDA|PDA]]、[[智慧手機|智慧手機]]或是其他[[移动设备|移动设备]]造成的[[重複使力傷害|重複使力傷害]]。黑莓拇指得名於1999年出現的智慧手機品牌[[BlackBerry|BlackBerry]]<ref>[http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/news/fullstory_65822.html ] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080821205306/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/news/fullstory_65822.html |date=21 August 2008 }}</ref>，不過也存在其他的名稱，例如{{le|Wiiitis|Wiiitis}}<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Nett MP, Collins MS, Sperling JW |title=Magnetic resonance imaging of acute "wiiitis" of the upper extremity |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_skeletal-radiology_2008-05_37_5/page/481 |journal=Skeletal Radiology |volume=37 |issue=5 |pages=481–83 |year=2008 |pmid=18259743 |doi=10.1007/s00256-008-0456-1}}</ref>、{{le|Nintendinitis|Nintendinitis}},<ref>{{cite journal |author=Koh TH |title=Ulcerative "nintendinitis": a new kind of repetitive strain injury |journal=The Medical Journal of Australia |volume=173 |issue=11–12 |pages=671 |date=December 2000 |pmid=11379534}}</ref>、PS拇指（Playstation thumb）、傳訊息拇指（texting thumb）<ref>{{cite web |author=Rush University Medical Center |url=https://www.rush.edu/health-wellness/discover-health/when-technology-hurts |title='Texting thumb' and other tech-related pain, explained |publisher=Rush University Medical Center |date=1 August 2012 |accessdate=2015-04-11 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025061056/https://www.rush.edu/health-wellness/discover-health/when-technology-hurts |dead-url=no }}</ref>、手機拇指（cellphone thumb）<ref>{{cite journal |author=Karim SA |title=From 'playstation thumb' to 'cellphone thumb': the new epidemic in teenagers |journal=South African Medical Journal |volume=99 |issue=3 |pages=161–2 |date=March 2009 |pmid=19563092}}</ref>、智慧手機拇指（smartphone thumb）、Android拇指（Android thumb）及iPhone拇指（iPhone thumb）。

黑莓拇指的症狀包括姆指及手腕的疼痛<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/04/22/AR2005042201739.html | work=The Washington Post | title=For Some, Thumb Pain Is BlackBerry's Stain | first=Amy | last=Joyce | date=2005-04-23 | accessdate=2010-04-03 | archive-date=2017-01-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129230909/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/04/22/AR2005042201739.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，嚴重的話，會讓有症狀的手暫時無法施力，尤其是無法握東西<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2005/10/69294 |title=The Agony of 'BlackBerry Thumb' |publisher=Wired.com |date=2005-10-21 |accessdate=2010-05-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419052633/http://www.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2005/10/69294 |archivedate=2010-04-19}}</ref>。

有關黑莓拇指的一個假想原因是拇指沒有像其他手指一様的{{le|精細動作|dexterity}}能力，不適合高速的[[盲打|盲打]]，若勉強使用就容易出現問題<ref>{{cite web |url=http://arthritis.webmd.com/news/20050126/BlackBerry-thumb-real-illness-just-dumb |title=BlackBerry Thumb: Real Illness or Just Dumb? |publisher=Arthritis.webmd.com |date=26 January 2005 |accessdate=2010-05-18 |archive-date=2010-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514205431/http://arthritis.webmd.com/news/20050126/blackberry-thumb-real-illness-just-dumb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

